nit: IMO this is neater with `ExecEraseStatement` removed and 

```cpp
    if (!m_database.m_db) return false;
    assert(stmt);

    // Bind: leftmost parameter in statement is index 1
    if (!stmt->Bind(1, blob, "key")) return false;
```

repeated in `EraseKey` and `ErasePrefix`,  in total it's only ~2 more LOC.

